PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the MUSKOWEKWAN BAND, of land situated in the rural municipalities of Kellross No. 247 or Emerald No. 277, Province of Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included in all cases but one, as follows: some 259 hectares (ha) as Muskowekwan Indian Reserve No. 85-40, 124 ha as Reserve 85-42, 65 ha as Reserve 85-45, 65 ha as Reserve 85-47 and 64 ha as Reserve 85-48.
